reviews.review_text: What a long Strange Trip it Was Funny how much you forget over time, but Thanks to the LMA I can jog my bad memory. By this time I was down to 3-5 shows a year after tearing it up in the mid 80's. I totally forgot about R&C and new Speedway Boogie, never have gotten these tapes, but man did the memories come back. I did a cursory soundcheck and this AUD seems to be the best of all posted. Still trying to find the Crap Center show with the Dew that shut up the Frat Boy security detail..

R&C CROWD GOES NUTS!



and they gave em good reason too
